{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "e94ca80a-0946-4740-b8f7-9acdcceebd6f",
    "name": "MindFlow API",
    "description": "Coleção de testes para o backend REST do MindFlow. Disciplina LDAMD — PUC Minas 2026/1.\n\nComo usar:\n1. Suba a infraestrutura: `podman compose up -d`\n2. Rode o backend: `mvn spring-boot:run`\n3. Execute 'Registrar Paciente' ou 'Registrar Psicólogo'\n4. O token JWT é salvo automaticamente na variável `{{token}}`\n5. Todas as demais requisições usam o token automaticamente",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "35576841"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar Paciente",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('pacienteUsuarioId', res.userId);",
                  "pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Token retornado', () => pm.expect(res.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('Perfil é PACIENTE', () => pm.expect(res.perfil).to.eql('PACIENTE'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"João Silva\",\n  \"email\": \"joao@email.com\",\n  \"senha\": \"123456\",\n  \"perfil\": \"PACIENTE\",\n  \"dadosPaciente\": {\n    \"telefone\": \"(31) 99999-0000\",\n    \"dataNascimento\": \"1995-06-15\",\n    \"formaPagamentoPref\": \"PIX\",\n    \"observacoesSaude\": \"Ansiedade leve\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/registrar",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "registrar"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
